overview: Price Brown was living the good life. He could buy anything he wanted… On someone else’s dime. Price later finds out that his actions don’t come without future repercussions. After receiving a tip from a local bum running the same scam, two Detectives are hot on his trail. One step ahead of the Detectives, he seeks refuge in his cousin’s frat house. Little did he know, his cousin has a secret of his own.
title: Frat House XO
